1.0.name: wordpress/tactile-crm-contact-form
1.0.description:
This plugin allows you to easily push contact form information from Wordpress into your Tactile CRM account. Tactile CRM is a simple, easy to use CRM for small businesses and you can signup for free at http://www.tactilecrm.com using the code WORDPRESS.

The new version tries to identify existing organisations and contacts before creating new ones.
